# 🏗️ Project Architecture Guide

## 📁 Directory Structure
- **Main Entry Point**: [src/main.tsx](mdc:move-magic-checklist-main/src/main.tsx) - React application bootstrap
- **App Component**: [src/App.tsx](mdc:move-magic-checklist-main/src/App.tsx) - Main application wrapper with providers
- **Configuration**: [vite.config.ts](mdc:move-magic-checklist-main/vite.config.ts) - Vite build configuration
- **Styling**: [tailwind.config.ts](mdc:move-magic-checklist-main/tailwind.config.ts) - Tailwind CSS configuration

## 🎯 Core Directories
- `src/components/` - Reusable UI components
  - `src/components/ui/` - shadcn/ui base components
  - `src/components/Header.tsx` - Navigation header
  - `src/components/ChecklistSection.tsx` - Main checklist functionality
- `src/pages/` - Page components (Index, Moving, Furniture, NotFound)
- `src/hooks/` - Custom React hooks (useAuth, use-mobile)
- `src/integrations/supabase/` - Database client and types
- `src/lib/` - Utility functions

## 🔧 Technology Stack
- **Frontend**: React 18 + TypeScript + Vite
- **UI Library**: shadcn/ui + Radix UI + Tailwind CSS
- **State Management**: React Query + Context API
- **Backend**: Supabase (PostgreSQL + Auth + RLS)
- **Routing**: React Router DOM
- **Icons**: Lucide React

## 🚀 Key Features
- **Checklist Management**: D-Day based moving checklist
- **User Authentication**: Google OAuth via Supabase
- **Real-time Data**: Supabase real-time subscriptions
- **Responsive Design**: Mobile-first approach
- **Service Integration**: Moving/cleaning services, furniture shopping